text: John Cockburn-Hood (16 January 1844 - 30 August 1902) was an English cricketer. He played nineteen first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1864 and 1869. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1844 births Category:1902 deaths Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney Category:Gentlemen of England cricketers Category:English cricketers of 1864 to 1889
